    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>尊敬的用户，您好。 </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>欢迎您致电梦线服务中心。 </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>我们致力为每一位漫游者用户提供最优质的梦境服务。 </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>那么，请问有什么可以帮您？</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039020/extras/4127c8115fd8a7327b5c744d277cfb32.avif?t=1746451761\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039020/extras_big/4127c8115fd8a7327b5c744d277cfb32.avif?t=1746451761 width=800 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《梦线404》是一款实验性质的短篇解谜游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深夜，你被一条来自“梦线服务中心”的短信吵醒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“恭喜您，中奖啦！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大概是钓鱼短信吧。你如此想着。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而短信中的乱码与内容的怪异，似乎勾起了你的好奇心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在，你的手中只有一部手机，一条神秘短信，和一个可能改变一切的电话号码。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好拨打这条未知的热线了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039020/extras/ca450c4b2f1e685e42197ceab45a2f9e.avif?t=1746451761\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039020/extras_big/ca450c4b2f1e685e42197ceab45a2f9e.avif?t=1746451761 width=800 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以尽情感受来自漫游者用户的不同梦境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配合原创音乐集，在五彩斑斓的梦境中感受内心的宁静吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039020/extras/f7e598ded4960ac1674f4c0e56329643.avif?t=1746451761\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039020/extras_big/f7e598ded4960ac1674f4c0e56329643.avif?t=1746451761 width=800 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>记住，梦线服务中心是您梦境旅程中唯一的朋友。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i> 我们是梦线服务中心，在提升梦境体验的道路上，我们竭诚为您提供最优质的服务。 </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>我们是梦线服务中心，Where all your dreams are not just your dreams :)</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039020/extras/99651fa13d507166a984b5e99bb94d60.avif?t=1746451761\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039020/extras_big/99651fa13d507166a984b5e99bb94d60.avif?t=1746451761 width=800 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操作方法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039020/extras/606d685ef6fb24478903e989ea66f184.avif?t=1746451761\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039020/extras_big/606d685ef6fb24478903e989ea66f184.avif?t=1746451761 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>联系我们</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· 策划 美术 叙事  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >@Blu  <a href=\"mailto:Daydreaminblu_studio@outlook.com\">Daydreaminblu_studio@outlook.com</a></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· 程序  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >@VoidCatt  <a href=\"mailto:voidcattdev@gmail.com\">voidcattdev@gmail.com</a></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· 音乐</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > @Yellow  <a href=\"mailto:yunhaohwang@gmail.com\">yunhaohwang@gmail.com</a></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特别鸣谢</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英文本地化 by <strong>Max Ponoroff</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
